
Further JOIN help..

ADD       Add a board, or newsgroup, to your NEW scan.
DELETE    Remove a board, or newsgroup, from your NEW scan.
FORUMS    Show a listing of newsgroups & local forums.
LIST      Show all boards you are subscribed to.
HELP      You be reading it, son.
QUIT      Exit back to the BBS areas.

For further information on Usenet, type HELP USENET at the main BBS
prompt. Proper etiquette must be followed when posting to Usenet, or
your account WILL be removed from the system.
